<subSubSection pageId="144" pageNumber="145" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="144" pageNumber="145">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="144" pageNumber="145">This species ranges along the mountains paralleling the Pacific Coast from southeastern Alaska along the British Columbia border (Lindroth 1961a: 86) and Kluane National Park in southwestern Yukon Territory (David H. Kavanaugh pers. comm. 2010) to west-central Oregon (Kavanaugh 1978: 811).</paragraph>
